<br>
I have been using the flash/fear to give my pet time to chew on the MOBs backside for a while to great success lately in DSP on the Stonegrabbers.  I have also noticed a few quirks.  <br>
<br>
For instance, if their fear path takes them toward you they can eventually get close enough to attack again while still blind.  <br>
<br>
Also, some MOBs (DSP Rockhoppers) will not always run away at all, but keep chasing you regardless of how far away you are.  The pet keeps chewing on their tails though so I am not complaining...<br>
<br>
